FAQs
What are the top universities to study in Turkey?

Some of the top universities include Boğaziçi University, Middle East Technical University, Istanbul University, and Koç University.
Do I need to know Turkish to study in Turkey?

Many programs are offered in English, but learning basic Turkish can be beneficial for daily life and integration.
What documents are needed to apply to study in Turkey?

You will need academic transcripts, proof of language proficiency, letters of recommendation, a personal statement, a valid passport, and passport-sized photographs.
